text: Naitasiri is one of the 14 provinces of Fiji. It is on Viti Levu, Fiji's largest island. It is part of the Central Division. Naitasiri has an area of . About 178,000 people lived there in 2017. The main town is Nasinu. The Medrausucu mountain ranges are in the province. Category:Provinces of Fiji
title: Naitasiri Province
